# Contribution Guidelines

We welcome thoughtful contributions to improve the Adaptive AI Fitness Coach Prompt.

## What You Can Do
- Add modules (e.g. sleep tracking, mindfulness, sport-specific flows)
- Improve tone/style variants for personality types
- Suggest behavior triggers and smart nudges
- Submit optimized nutrition tracking or feedback models

## Rules
- All contributions must retain the EGAP+ clause
- Clearly document behavioral logic
- Submit PRs with examples and test cases
- Use Markdown, plain English, and prompt-friendly structures

## Attributions
Please retain clear authorship to Mateusz Korsak "(https://www.linkedin.com/in/korsakmateusz/)" with any derivative versions.

Thank you for helping make this system better and smarter.
